cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and natural language processing, which suggests that it belongs to the cs.CV and cs.CL sub-categories. The use of artificial tokens to control language is a technique that falls under the umbrella of machine learning, which could also place this paper in the cs.LG and cs.AI sub-categories. Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on generating captions for images, which is a task that falls under the cs.MM sub-category.
